headline: 7.3 Million Tuned In to Debate in Iowa
abstract: Ratings results from the debate in Iowa.
lead_paragraph: DES MOINES â€” Six and a half months ago, with the Iowa caucuses a speck in the distance, roughly 18 million Americans paused their evenings to watch a group of Democratic presidential candidates debate onstage in Miami, a record audience for a televised Democratic matchup.
